{"tid":1895620,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[告急]3月執笠黃店!!!","createTime":"2020-02-24T15:48:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T10:03:55.000Z","uid":71179,"like":16,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1762f580bf40977d89516fb6c8c88ee85dfb0b85","tid":1895620,"uid":71179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T15:48:38.000Z","msg":"今晚同女朋友去食飯<br />\n佢同我講依間係旺角嘅黃店就執<br />\n去到見到好多人係門口排隊<br />\n我估都係咁多位巴打去撐黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n坐低啲野食都唔錯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t0wXq7H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft0wXq7H.jpg&h=9a08ab56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有個自助吧可以無限食串燒甜品<br />\n去到個一刻<br />\n我都覺得ok<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但係</span><br />\n當我係自助區拎野食果陣<br />\n我竟然見到佢個氣炸鍋底<br />\n全部都係曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對唔住咁多位大佬<br />\n我無圖<br />\n唔好問候我老母<br />\n淨係想提吓咁多位巴打 有時啲餐廳係無得盲撐 啲野食難食 衛生環境惡劣 其實執硬<br />\n我想係度跪求<br />\n高質黃店<br />\n三萬thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef7cfdc1d225bcb21508deb296e3252bae26a0d0","tid":1895620,"uid":209773,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T15:49:59.000Z","msg":"全部都係曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n離譜咗啲"},{"pid":"284446db51029e819cf7fab691f29bd75c1a6831","tid":1895620,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T15:51:00.000Z","msg":"樓主屌黃店<br />\n屍屍tai會進場屌你<br />\n樓主快啲走, 幫你頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},