<br />\n鳩up唔洗本<br />\n<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"af3230866f60562f3eb1e4937f5c4c9a3a882857","tid":1895620,"uid":5103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T16:46:19.000Z","msg":"我地小隊依家正努力整合緊屬於我地香港本土YouTube channel<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打們可以支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n攻擊重要,防守都好重要<br />\n如果出面做攻擊,我地會做好防守依一個環節<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地都仲有一班本土channel須要我地大力支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">目標對每個本土channel：subscibe+㩒鐘仔+share俾10個fd+睇片+留言+like </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">覺唔覺得香港真係無乜本土YouTube Channel? (2.1)</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1886497\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1886497</a>"},{"pid":"804813cf0a5d9e4b59acd8084745b82fa38b7ddb","tid":1895620,"uid":107671,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T16:49:38.000Z","msg":"餐廳有甲由好正常<br />\n見唔到就當冇架啦<br />\n不過你見到就冇計啦，都食左落肚啦，咪當補補佢囉<br />\n<br />\n出街食野唔好亂咁搵野睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b37cd0ee79e7cd08078dd1e1d285c288c59f2fc8","tid":1895620,"uid":71179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"804813cf0a5d9e4b59acd8084745b82fa38b7ddb","tid":1895620,"uid":107671,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T16:49:38.000Z","msg":"餐廳有甲由好正常<br />\n見唔到就當冇架啦<br />\n不過你見到就冇計啦，都食左落肚啦，咪當補補佢囉<br />\n<br />\n出街食野唔好亂咁搵野睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T16:54:49.000Z","msg":"一場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.g